WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:04.160
What are you doing, Claire?

2
00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:07.860
Oh, boss.

3
00:00:07.860 --> 00:00:10.859
Do you have feelings from Miss Newton?

4
00:00:10.859 --> 00:00:12.339
Yes.

5
00:00:12.339 --> 00:00:18.339
Okay, she is the only one that I love, and she's also going to be the last one that I love.

6
00:00:18.339 --> 00:00:22.370
I might be overstepping my boundaries by saying this, but...

7
00:00:22.370 --> 00:00:25.370
Why don't you just tell her the way you feel about her?

8
00:00:25.370 --> 00:00:28.370
Because she hates me.

9
00:00:28.370 --> 00:00:33.289
You know what? I have a plan.

10
00:00:33.289 --> 00:00:35.289
I want you to go buy the house.

11
00:00:35.289 --> 00:00:37.289
And the same neighborhood is her...

12
00:00:37.289 --> 00:00:39.289
Right next to where her house is.

13
00:00:39.289 --> 00:00:41.320
Can you do that?

14
00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:46.640
Yes, sir.

15
00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.640
I can't see anything clearly again.

16
00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:51.469
Why didn't he want me to see him?

17
00:00:51.469 --> 00:00:54.560
Mysterious call, boy.

18
00:00:54.560 --> 00:01:02.030
You scared me.

19
00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:03.219
Yeah?

20
00:01:03.219 --> 00:01:06.209
Yeah.

21
00:01:06.209 --> 00:01:07.689
I missed you.

22
00:01:07.689 --> 00:01:39.959
Good of seeing you.

